            h3 Interview
            p I will meet with you to get a deeper understanding of exactly what you’re looking for. We will talk through your goals, visions, dreams, logistics, budget and much more.

        .m-process-step-item.odd
          .m-process-icon-content
            .m-process-icon
          .m-process-copy-content
            h3 Observation
            p I will do an initial observation of your site;  its soil types, microclimates, patterns, cycles, wildlife habits and existing habitats. I will also sketch your home; it’s layout, orientation, scale, microclimates, opening, use and views. 
        .m-process-step-item
          .m-process-icon-content
            .m-process-icon
          .m-process-copy-content
            h3 Site Analysis
            p Using technology and observation, I will bring together climatic, habitat and topographic data for you site, and use this as the basis of my design process. This will include a range of analyses&mdash;from wind direction and speed, to soil composition and native plant species.
        span.line#discover
        hr.m-process-divider

      .m-process-wrapper
