            h2 2. Design

        .m-process-step-item.odd
          .m-process-icon-content
            .m-process-icon
          .m-process-copy-content
            h3 Conceptual Design
            p Using all aspects of the discovery phase, I will come up with one or more initial designs for your site. This design will bring together all elements into one unified design, each one connected and benefitting from another. If you are also designing a new home, this phase will also include conceptual drawings from the architect who I will have work alongside. 
        .m-process-step-item
          .m-process-icon-content
            .m-process-icon
          .m-process-copy-content
            h3 Detailed Design
            p There will most likely be some back and forths with the conceptual design, but once we have landed on something we are all happy with, I will draw a detailed design. This is the final stage before implementation and the drawings will be ready to hand over to the landscapers. 
